content.html: I don't care if #Log4J is supposed to be pronounced as Log-Forge... ...I'm still gonna pronounce it as Log-Four-Jay. Same way that Nginx is not Engine-Ex, it's En-Ginx (G pronounced like the G in gif).
content.value:
I don't care if #Log4J is supposed to be pronounced as Log-Forge...

...I'm still gonna pronounce it as Log-Four-Jay.

Same way that Nginx is not Engine-Ex, it's En-Ginx (G pronounced like the G in gif).
